SIMPLE: homeliness
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Homeliness
<hw>Home"li*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Homely</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Domesticity; care of home.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧Wifely <xex>homeliness</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Familiarity; intimacy.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Plainness; want of elegance or beauty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>Coarseness; simplicity; want of refinement; <as>as,
the <ex>homeliness</ex> of manners, or language</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Homeling</ent>⟦br⟧
